description:
We can see why this photo has been shared all over. How incredible! 

Repost image and caption from @hannahillphotography:
Another all time favorite! Dad catching baby after a long and powerful labor and birth! #BTS the Midwife actually just stepped right out of frame for a millisecond after helping mom push and make sure head was safely out before leaving it all for Dad to finish the “catch and lift.”
You can see a little darker shadow on the blinds where I edited the small bit of her hand that was still in the shot.  These types of moments are pretty rare and I’m so honored to have gotten to witness and capture this moment for this dad, mom and their baby girl! This one has won a few birth photography awards too! And has been featured all over the world! #signatureshots #hannahillphotography
